title SPA new note
browser->server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
note over server:
The request's Content-Type header tells the server 
that the included data is represented in JSON format.
Without this header, the server would not know 
how to correctly parse the data.
end note
server-->browser:  code 201 Created
note over browser:
the browser stays on the same page 
and does not send any more HTTP requests.
end note
